---
// Community Message Component - Heartfelt message from OIAC leadership
---

<style>
@keyframes shine {
    0% { background-position: -200% center; }
    100% { background-position: 200% center; }
}

@keyframes fade-in {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.quote-card {
    animation: fade-in 1s ease-out forwards;
}

.golden-border {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #D4AF37, transparent);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
}

.golden-border:hover {
    animation: shine 3s linear infinite;
}

.arabic-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Naskh Arabic', 'Traditional Arabic', 'Arabic Typesetting', serif;
    direction: rtl;
}

.signature {
    font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive, serif;
}

.decorative-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4AF37, #B8941F);
    border-radius: 50%;
}
</style>

<section class="py-16 px-4 md:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-softBeige-50 to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <!-- Quote Card -->
        <div class="quote-card bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Golden Border Top -->
            <div class="golden-border h-1"></div>

            <!-- Content -->
            <div class="p-8 md:p-12">
                <!-- Opening Quote Mark -->
                <div class="text-6xl md:text-7xl text-terracottaRed-200 leading-none mb-4">"</div>

                <!-- Arabic Greeting -->
                <div class="mb-6 text-center">
                    <h3 class="arabic-text text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-800 font-semibold mb-2">
                        السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sageGreen text-lg font-medium">As'Salamu'Alaykum Dear OIAC Family</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Decorative Divider -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
                    <div class="decorative-dot"></div>
                    <div class="decorative-dot"></div>
                    <div class="decorative-dot"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Main Message -->
                <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
                    <p class="text-center md:text-left">
                        <strong class="text-emerald-600">Alhamdulillah</strong>, with the help of <strong>Allah ﷻ</strong> and through your generosity, our recent fundraising dinner for the dream Southside Islamic School was a beautiful success.
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-center md:text-left">
                        Together, we raised <strong class="text-terracottaRed text-xl">$2.8 million</strong>, a remarkable step that brings us closer to making this long-awaited vision a reality, <strong class="text-emerald-600">InshaAllah</strong>, by <strong>September 2026</strong>.
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-center md:text-left">
                        The door of participation is still open. You can join us and be part of this <strong class="text-amber-600">legacy</strong> — a legacy that will serve your children and the generations to come with strong Islamic education and values.
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-center md:text-left italic bg-softBeige/30 p-4 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-terracottaRed">
                        Every donation, every share, every dua, and every effort is a brick in this foundation. Together, as one community, we are building a future where our children can grow with both excellence in education and strength in faith.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Decorative Divider -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 my-8">
                    <div class="decorative-dot"></div>
                    <div class="decorative-dot"></div>
                    <div class="decorative-dot"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Closing Dua -->
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sageGreen-50 via-emerald-50 to-sageGreen-50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6">
                    <p class="text-center text-gray-800 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        <strong>Jazakum Allahu khayran</strong> for your unwavering love, sacrifices, and dedication.
                    </p>
                    <p class="arabic-text text-center text-xl md:text-2xl text-sageGreen mt-3 font-semibold">
                        جزاكم الله خيراً
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-center text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base mt-4 italic">
                        May Allah ﷻ accept from you, increase you in blessings, and unite us all in Jannah alongside His Prophet ﷺ.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Signature -->
                <div class="text-center md:text-right">
                    <div class="inline-block">
                        <p class="signature text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-600 mb-1">Your OIAC Family</p>
                        <div class="h-0.5 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-terracottaRed to-transparent"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Closing Quote Mark -->
                <div class="text-right text-6xl md:text-7xl text-terracottaRed-200 leading-none mt-4">"</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Golden Border Bottom -->
            <div class="golden-border h-1"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom Action -->
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
            <a
                href="/donatetonewcentre"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600 hover:from-amber-600 hover:to-amber-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 text-base md:text-lg"
            >
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
                </svg>
                Join This Legacy Today
            </a>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3">Together, we build the future</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
